{
    "poem_title": "- CI - A don Fray Diego de Mardones, obispo de Córdoba, dedicándole el maestro Risco un libro de música ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": true,
    "author": "Gongora",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Un culto Risco en venas hoy süaves",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "conceptuosamente se desata,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "cuyo néctar, no ya líquida plata,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+-+++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "hace canoras aun las piedras graves.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un culto Risco en venas hoy süaves\nconceptuosamente se desata,\ncuyo néctar, no ya líquida plata,\nhace canoras aun las piedras graves."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Tú, pues, que el pastoral callado sabes",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+----+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "con mano administrar al cielo grata,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "de vestir, digno, manto de escarlata,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--++-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "y de heredar a Pedro en las dos llaves,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+--++-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tú, pues, que el pastoral callado sabes\ncon mano administrar al cielo grata,\nde vestir, digno, manto de escarlata,\ny de heredar a Pedro en las dos llaves,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "este, si numeroso, dulce escucha",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+----+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "torrente, que besar desea la playa",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "de tus ondas, ¡oh mar!, siempre serenas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+-+++--+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "este, si numeroso, dulce escucha\ntorrente, que besar desea la playa\nde tus ondas, ¡oh mar!, siempre serenas."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "Si el armonioso leño silva mucha",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "atraer pudo vocal, Risco atraya",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-++--++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "un Mar, dones hoy todo a sus arenas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+++-++---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si el armonioso leño silva mucha\natraer pudo vocal, Risco atraya\nun Mar, dones hoy todo a sus arenas."
        }
    ]
}